14#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_SMIMEA_53_C
15#define RDATA_GENERIC_SMIMEA_53_C
16
17#define RRTYPE_SMIMEA_ATTRIBUTES 0
18
19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_smimea(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21
22 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
23
24 return (generic_fromtext_tlsa(rdclass, type, lexer, origin, options,
25 target, callbacks));
26}
27
28static inline isc_result_t
29totext_smimea(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
30
31 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
32
33 return (generic_totext_tlsa(rdata, tctx, target));
34}
35
36static inline isc_result_t
37fromwire_smimea(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
38
39 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
40
41 return (generic_fromwire_tlsa(rdclass, type, source, dctx, options,
42 target));
43}
44
45static inline isc_result_t
46towire_smimea(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
47 isc_region_t sr;
48
49 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
50 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
51
52 UNUSED(cctx);
53
54 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
55 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
56}
57
58static inline int
59compare_smimea(ARGS_COMPARE) {
60 isc_region_t r1;
61 isc_region_t r2;
62
63 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
64 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
65 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
66 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
67 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
68
69 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
70 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
71 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
72}
73
74static inline isc_result_t
75fromstruct_smimea(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
76
77 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
78
79 return (generic_fromstruct_tlsa(rdclass, type, source, target));
80}
81
82static inline isc_result_t
83tostruct_smimea(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
84 dns_rdata_smimea_t *smimea = target;
85
86 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
87 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
88
89 smimea->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
90 smimea->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
91 ISC_LINK_INIT(&smimea->common, link);
92
93 return (generic_tostruct_tlsa(rdata, target, mctx));
94}
95
96static inline void
97freestruct_smimea(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
98 dns_rdata_smimea_t *smimea = source;
99
100 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
101 REQUIRE(smimea->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
102
103 generic_freestruct_tlsa(source);
104}
105
106static inline isc_result_t
107additionaldata_smimea(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
108 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
109
110 UNUSED(rdata);
111 UNUSED(add);
112 UNUSED(arg);
113
114 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
115}
116
117static inline isc_result_t
118digest_smimea(ARGS_DIGEST) {
119 isc_region_t r;
120
121 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
122
123 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
124
125 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
126}
127
128static inline bool
129checkowner_smimea(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
130
131 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
132
133 UNUSED(name);
134 UNUSED(type);
135 UNUSED(rdclass);
136 UNUSED(wildcard);
137
138 return (true);
139}
140
141static inline bool
142checknames_smimea(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
143
144 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_smimea);
145
146 UNUSED(rdata);
147 UNUSED(owner);
148 UNUSED(bad);
149
150 return (true);
151}
152
153static inline int
154casecompare_smimea(ARGS_COMPARE) {
155 return (compare_smimea(rdata1, rdata2));
156}

158#endif /* RDATA_GENERIC_SMIMEA_53_C */
